each element in a map has a key and a value.
each element in a set has only a key.in other words,the key in a set is the value.

when I want to record what words in a paragraph appear,I would use set.(1 dimension)
when I want to record how many times each distinct word appear in the paragraph,I would use map.(2 dimensions.)

